# Commit these project files
# - Source, tests, and static assets: src/, tests/, public/, favicon_io/
# - Site entry files: index.html, 404.html, browse.html, videos.html
# - Runtime assets/config meant for deployment: manifest.json, service-worker.js, .htaccess
# - Package metadata and lockfiles: package.json, package-lock.json
# - CI and docs: .github/, README.md, CHANGELOG.md

